item.title: Week -2
item.description: The end of may is quite busy for me. I have to finish some projects on my University before the end of month, to be sure that I will able to spend enough time on GSoC. Everything is on track, so there’s no reason to worry. At the weekend I’m going to spend time on looking into SymPy, especially into diffgeom module. I would like to find some idea, witch could be use in my project.
